      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be validated under an FDA-recognized quality management system with full version-controlled test suite and documented regression testing.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver operates under ISO 9001 QMS with version control; however, the hemolysis damage model sub-module lacks an independent regression test suite. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
