      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation protocols with independent review of setup parameters; checklist-based QA on boundary condition assignment.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup documented in internal technical report; independent review performed by one reviewer. Formal checklist not used; reviewer lacked hemolysis modeling expertise. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
    },
