      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis model form must be justified by mechanistic evidence; power-law damage accumulation models must be validated against cell-level experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger model adopted. Model form justified by literature survey referencing the calibration study cited in this package (see referencesIdentifier). Cell-level validation data not obtained independently. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
