      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have traceable experimental sources with uncertainty characterization; Monte Carlo distributions must be justified.",
      "rationale": "Viscosity and density inputs are well-characterized. Hemolysis model exponent and threshold stress parameters drawn from literature with wide uncertainty ranges; distributions assumed uniform due to lack of data. Monte Carlo performed but input distributions are poorly constrained. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
