      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must represent physiological variability in blood rheology across donor population; minimum n=10 independent donors required.",
      "rationale": "Experimental validation data used glycerol-water analog; no biological donor variability characterization performed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 2 by proxy; formal assessment not completed."
